io.github.msdk.datamodel.rawdata

Interface RawDataFile

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    WritableRawDataFile

    public interface RawDataFile
    Raw data file, typically obtained by loading data from one of the supported file formats. A raw data file is a collection of scans (MsScan).
    See Also:
    MsScan
